---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Boundless Travelogues">
  <section class="container fade-in" style="max-width: 900px;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Last Updated: November 17, 2025</p>
    
    <div style="line-height: 1.8;">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information that you provide directly to us when booking tours or contacting us:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Personal identification information (Name, Email, Phone Number, Address)</li>
        <li>Travel preferences and requirements</li>
        <li>Payment information (processed securely through payment gateways)</li>
        <li>Health information (if disclosed for safety purposes)</li>
        <li>ID proof documents for booking verification</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To process and manage your tour bookings</li>
        <li>To communicate with you about your trips</li>
        <li>To provide customer support</li>
        <li>To send promotional offers (with your consent)</li>
        <li>To improve our services</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">3. Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share your information with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Hotels, transport providers, and tour operators to fulfill your bookings</li>
        <li>Payment processors for secure transactions</li>
        <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">4. Data Security</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information</li>
        <li>Payment information is processed through secure, encrypted channels</li>
        <li>Access to personal data is restricted to authorized personnel only</li>
        <li>We regularly review our security practices</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">5. Your Rights</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Access your personal information we hold</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your information (subject to legal requirements)</li>
        <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">6. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We may use cookies to improve website functionality</li>
        <li>Analytics tools help us understand user behavior</li>
        <li>You can disable cookies in your browser settings</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">7. Data Retention</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We retain your information for as long as necessary to provide services</li>
        <li>Booking records are kept for 7 years for legal and tax purposes</li>
        <li>Marketing data is retained until you opt-out</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Our services are not directed to children under 13</li>
        <li>We do not knowingly collect information from children</li>
        <li>Parental consent is required for minors traveling</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">9. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We may update this policy periodically</li>
        <li>Changes will be posted on this page</li>
        <li>Continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of changes</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">10. Image Usage and Attribution</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Destination images displayed on our website are sourced from multiple websites and online resources</li>
        <li>These images are not photographed by Boundless Travelogues unless specifically mentioned</li>
        <li>Images are used for promotional and informational purposes to showcase destinations</li>
        <li>We respect intellectual property rights and will remove any image upon legitimate copyright claim</li>
        <li>Personal photos taken during tours may be used for marketing with participant consent</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">11. Customer Reviews and Testimonials</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Reviews displayed on our website are personal responses received directly from our clients</li>
        <li>Some testimonials are sourced from existing Google reviews of Boundless Travelogues</li>
        <li>All reviews represent genuine feedback from actual customers who have used our services</li>
        <li>We may edit reviews for length or clarity while maintaining the original sentiment</li>
        <li>Client names and personal details in reviews may be modified to protect privacy</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">12. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related questions or to exercise your rights, contact us:</p>
      <div style="background-color: #1a1a1a; border: 2px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 1rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);">
        <p style="color: #e8eaed;"><strong style="color: #00D4FF;">Phone:</strong> +91 8078107622</p>
        <p style="color: #e8eaed;"><strong style="color: #00D4FF;">Email:</strong> boundlesstravelogues@gmail.com</p>
        <p style="color: #e8eaed;"><strong style="color: #00D4FF;">Address:</strong> Kerala, India</p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
